== 製作 ==
=== 開發 ===
2014年10月24日，{{le|TBS (電視頻道)|TBS (U.S. TV channel)|TBS}}預訂了由喬登·希普利與賈斯汀·希普利撰寫，被譽為喜劇版《[[迷失|Lost檔案]]》的單鏡喜劇試播集，由傑西·何拉製作，<ref name="Pilot Order">{{cite web |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |date=2014-10-24 |url=http://deadline.com/2014/10/wrecked-pilot-tbs-lost-859085/ |title=TBS Orders ‘Wrecked’ Deserted Island Comedy Pilot That Echoes ‘Lost’ |work=Deadline.com |access-date=2016-07-09 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205040840/https://deadline.com/2014/10/wrecked-pilot-tbs-lost-859085/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>預計於[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]展開拍攝。<ref name="Cast"/>本劇被描述為《Lost檔案》與《[[酒吧五傑|酒吧五傑]]》的集合體，故事將講述一台飛機失事於荒島上，倖存的乘客將在島上面臨各種威脅與考驗。<ref name="Pilot Order"/>

2015年5月13日，[[特納電視網|TNT]]與TBS主席身兼透納娛樂首席內容官的{{le|凱文·賴利|Kevin Reilly (executive)}}正式給予本劇10集系列預訂，由《[[廢柴聯盟|廢柴聯盟]]》、《[[幸福結局|好友行不行]]》摩西·波特擔任節目統籌，並與何拉共同擔任執行製作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/turner-upfront-tnt-tbs-load-up-shows-prep-for-daring-brand-makeovers-1201494119/|title=Turner Upfront: TNT, TBS Load Up On Shows, Prep For ‘Daring’ Brand Makeovers|publisher=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]|author=Cynthia Littleton|date=2015-05-13|accessdate=2017-04-26|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031022240/https://variety.com/2015/tv/news/turner-upfront-tnt-tbs-load-up-shows-prep-for-daring-brand-makeovers-1201494119/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=futonpress>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2015/05/13/kevin-reilly-unveils-bold-vision-for-tnt-and-tbs-at-turner-broadcastings-2015-upfront-407514/20150513turner03/ |title=Kevin Reilly Unveils Bold Vision for TNT & TBS At Turner Broadcasting's 2015 Upfront |date=2015-05-13 |publisher=富頓評論家 |access-date=2016-07-09 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713000545/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2015/05/13/kevin-reilly-unveils-bold-vision-for-tnt-and-tbs-at-turner-broadcastings-2015-upfront-407514/20150513turner03/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

